name: Emily Sinclair
review: Max is a fantastic instructor, providing in depth explanations of concepts to help you learn. I appreciate that in most instances he provides a starting and ending package to at first give you a boost, and then to allow you to compare or troubleshoot your own work against his.

name: Kuroko Tetsuya
review: Clear explanations with detailed practice exercises. However the test questions were a little difficult.
